"{\"uid\": \"oann.com-newsroom-chiles-could-be-stripped-of-bronze-medal-in-olympics-controversy-following-cas-ruling\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"OAN StaffSophia Flores1:45 PM - Saturday, August 10, 2024 The Court of Arbitration for Sport (CAS) ruled on Saturday that the United States' initial score inquiry regarding gymnast Jordan Chiles' final floor exercise routine was submitted after the deadline.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 259, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 3, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/One_America_News_Network\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"OAN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/One_America_News_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/One_America_News_Network\"}, {\"begin\": 127, \"end\": 140, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9997614343258638, \"rank\": 0.00015091352088879875, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 42, \"to\": 48}, {\"ngram\": \"The Court\", \"from\": 58, \"to\": 67}, {\"ngram\": \"Arbitration\", \"from\": 71, \"to\": 82}, {\"ngram\": \"Sport\", \"from\": 87, \"to\": 92}, {\"ngram\": \"CAS\", \"from\": 94, \"to\": 97}, {\"ngram\": \"Saturday\", \"from\": 108, \"to\": 116}, {\"ngram\": \"the deadline\", \"from\": 245, \"to\": 257}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As of Saturday morning, it is unclear what the score change means for Chiles' bronze medal.\", \"from\": 261, \"to\": 352, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Saturday morning\", \"from\": 267, \"to\": 283}, {\"ngram\": \"the score change\", \"from\": 304, \"to\": 320}, {\"ngram\": \"Chiles' bronze medal\", \"from\": 331, \"to\": 351}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With her score being reverted to the original 13.666, she returns to fifth place.\", \"from\": 353, \"to\": 434, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her score\", \"from\": 358, \"to\": 367}, {\"ngram\": \"fifth place\", \"from\": 422, \"to\": 433}]}, {\"sentence\": \"CAS determined that the inquiry submitted on behalf of Chiles was made after the one-minute deadline specified in the regulations and, therefore, has no effect on the final ranking.\", \"from\": 436, \"to\": 617, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 436, \"end\": 439, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Court_of_Arbitration_for_Sport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.373970503501648e-15, \"text\": \"CAS\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Court_of_Arbitration_for_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Court_of_Arbitration_for_Sport\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the inquiry\", \"from\": 456, \"to\": 467}, {\"ngram\": \"behalf\", \"from\": 481, \"to\": 487}, {\"ngram\": \"Chiles\", \"from\": 491, \"to\": 497}, {\"ngram\": \"the one-minute deadline\", \"from\": 513, \"to\": 536}, {\"ngram\": \"the regulations\", \"from\": 550, \"to\": 565}, {\"ngram\": \"no effect\", \"from\": 586, \"to\": 595}, {\"ngram\": \"the final ranking\", \"from\": 599, \"to\": 616}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After its ruling, CAS announced that the International Gymnastics Federation (FIG) will determine the final ranking.\", \"from\": 619, \"to\": 735, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 637, \"end\": 640, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Court_of_Arbitration_for_Sport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.373970503501648e-15, \"text\": \"CAS\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Court_of_Arbitration_for_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Court_of_Arbitration_for_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 660, \"end\": 701, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Gymnastics_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Gymnastics Federation (FIG)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resou